text.tspan: Homicide rate, by sex of the victim, 2021
Annual number of deaths from homicide per 100,000, for males and females. Countries above the diagonal line have a
higher male homicide rate, whereas countries below the line have a higher female homicide rate.
Data source: United Nations Office on Drugs and Crime (2023)
